## 🚀 Cara Menjalankan Project

### 1. Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/username/heart-disease-prediction-random-forest.git
```

Masuk ke folder project:

```bash
cd heart-disease-prediction-random-forest
```

---

### 2. Buat Virtual Environment

```bash
python3 -m venv venv
```

Aktifkan:

Mac/Linux

```bash
source venv/bin/activate
```

Windows

```bash
venv\Scripts\activate
```

---

### 3. Install Dependency

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

Atau:

```bash
pip install streamlit pandas numpy matplotlib seaborn scikit-learn joblib
```

---

### 4. Training Model

```bash
python train_model.py
```

Output:

```text
Akurasi Model : 98.54%
Model berhasil disimpan!
```

---

### 5. Menjalankan Dashboard

```bash
streamlit run app.py
```

atau

```bash
python -m streamlit run app.py
```

Dashboard akan berjalan pada:

```text
http://localhost:8501
```

---

